This documentation describes the Cloudflare Service Broker for Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF).
The Cloudflare Service Broker registers a service broker on PCF and exposes teh free service plan on the Marketplace.
Developers can provision domains on Cloudflare using the cf CLI.

## <a id='overview'></a>Overview

The Cloudflare Service Broker includes the following key features:

* Provisions a domain name on Cloudflare.

